# Per-service Gradle build artifacts — never commit (regenerated by every build/test run).
*/.gradle/
*/build/

# nba-model/rl_qnet.json is COMMITTED (the legacy validation Q-net, == databricks/ml/rl_qnet.json) so the
# Docker/compose build is self-contained (`docker compose up` needs no staging). run.ps1 -Build still stages the
# same file from databricks/ml; point it at a different model to override, but don't commit that override.
